<http://www.spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/event/23201APGCMPGJNLTBJBBRLRLRBCKNMGMV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "A Black History Showcase ";
  schema:description """
	The Power of Song: A Black History Showcase is a dynamic, culturally rich concert celebrating the myriad forms of Black music. Featuring talented student ensembles and faculty of Capilano University Jazz Studies Program alongside esteemed guest artists (TBA), the performance honors the profound historical impact and artistic evolution of the African diaspora.  
""";
